Join the UAE’s largest bank and one of the world’s largest and safest financial institutions. Our focus is to create value for our employees, customers, shareholders and communities to grow through differentiation, agility and innovation. We are looking for top talent and your success is our success. Accelerate your growth as you help us reach our goals and advance your career. Be ready to make your mark a top company, in an exciting &amp; dynamic industry. Job Purpose The individual is responsible for defining, owning and scaling the bank’s API‑led propositions across Global Trade, Treasury Services and Tokenized / Digital Asset‑enabled offerings. The role owns the strategic product vision, commercialization, monetization and enterprise‑wide adoption of API‑based capabilities, positioning APIs and Open Banking as a core distribution and engagement layer that embeds the bank into client ecosystems, enables real‑time financial flows and supports emerging use cases across the current and future state of transaction banking. The role acts as a strategic bridge between business, technology, digital transformation and regulatory bodies, ensuring that all API‑led products are client‑centric, scalable, secure and fully compliant with UAE and international regulatory frameworks. Key Accountabilities Contribute to the development and execution of GTx and Wholesale Banking API and Open banking strategy across domestic and international locations. Define and own the API product vision and long‑term roadmap aligned with Global Transaction Banking, Treasury and Tokenization strategy. Position API and Open Banking capabilities as core differentiator for payments, liquidity management, escrow services and Next Gen propositions Identify collaborate-to- create opportunities with Fintech partners for innovative use cases for Cash and Trade propositions. Drive harmonization and consistency across product lines to create a coherent, scalable API and Open Banking stack for all cash and 